By that statement either you are NOT agnostic, or you don't know what it means, or you don't know what you are.<br>
<br>
Agnostic takes no stance on the existance or non-existance of a higher power, basically believing that you are not pretentious(sp?) enough to say you know what is going on.  That is agnostic.  Thus you wouldn't care about saying it.<br>
<br>
